---+ Wikulu demo for 14.05.

A demo for Wikulu will be created. It will allow keyphrase extraction and text segmentation for !MediaWiki. It will also support search for a local installation of Simple Wikipedia. The search will be executed while the user is still typing.

---++ Steps

   * Install Simple !MediaWiki on mrburns
   * Install Wikulu for !MediaWiki on mrburns
   * Integrate live search into Wikulu
      * Create a bigger search field that can be invoked by clicking a button
      * The search field will execute a search after every word and display the results on the side of the search field.